verbose_text: In a parallel approach, we measured levels of GTP bound, activated CDC42 by performing pull-down assays with the CDC42 binding domain of Wiskott-Aldrich syndrome protein (WASP) fused to glutathione S-transferase (GST) (GST-WASP).
evidence: activated CDC42 by performing pull-down assays with the CDC42-binding domain of Wiskott-Aldrich syndrome protein
